name: printPaymentForm

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged into 'Review A/P Entries Payments' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Review A/P Entries,Payments}

testSteps.description: Then the'Payments' search page should show up
Then the payments search results should show up
Then the Supplier of the first payment search result should be '72552'
When i click on print button of the first search result
Then the payment successfully sent to print notification should show up
Then the file should be downloaded

title: Print payment form
